root: ^Okay lets head over to the gym with "roommate"
^"Time to lift some weights" roommate says

b:
^"Wow! You're so good!" roommate says

^"Thanks!"

^That was a really good gym session! I feel so much stronger!

^I feel so tired, I just want to give up

^I look over to the side, roommate is doing so well and you can't lift anything today

^I try to lift myself above the bar again, halfway you arms begin to give

^"UGH"

^You let go of the bar as roommate helps you

^"I think we should call it for a day."
